# Admin Console — Environment Variables

Copy ke `.env.local` di folder admin-console/

```env
# Backend API URL
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# Admin auth (basic protection sementara, Phase 5)
VITE_ADMIN_SECRET=your-admin-password-here
```

## Production (Vercel — project terpisah)
Set di Vercel → Project Settings → Environment Variables:
- `VITE_API_URL` = `https://finance-analyzer-a82j.onrender.com`
- `VITE_ADMIN_SECRET` = [password kuat]
